data.description: Back on the market! Featuring a brick front, two finished levels, a private driveway, four bedrooms, and 2.5 bathrooms, this tastefully remodeled semi-detached townhome welcomes you home. With a brand-new roof, new carpeting, and brand-new paint throughout, this home. You can locate the living room on the main level, which has LVP flooring, the dining room adjacent to the kitchen, which has ceramic tile flooring and a quartz countertop, the laundry room, and the door leading to the rear. Go up to the top floor to find four bedrooms and two complete bathrooms. Include the location's proximity to FedEx Field, the Wayne Curry Sports and Learning Complex, and the National Harbor. The area is also close to hotels, restaurants, and retail stores. DC, Alexandria, VA, and the National Harbor are all nearby.
